            <div class="detailed">
                <p>Leaves are beautiful with their varying colors in the fall. However, once they start falling and cover your lawn, they quickly become a weekends worth of raking and bagging.</p>
                <p>Lawn Enforcement, Inc will blow all leaves off of your lawn and beds and then vacuum them to remove the leaves from your property.  Leaf Removal charges are based on the time to remove the leaves.  Please call for a price quote.</p>

            </div>
        </div>

